node.text: Loved speaking to @chunkz on how @statsports GPS tracker has played a huge role in my career so far and how it can be the difference between making it or not!  Part 2 coming soon – where we talk  FIFA stats v real life stats  #TheDifference

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Phil Foden on July 13, 2021. May be an image of 3 people and people standing.

node.text:
Being part of this group has meant so much. Winning together, losing together and always sticking together. 

We're all hurting right now but the racist abuse sent to some of my teammates after the bravery they showed on Sunday night is disgusting and has no place in the game. 

We can't and won't let hate win.

It’s been a special summer, my first major tournament and I felt so much pride to wear that shirt. We felt your support all the way, I just wish it could've ended the way we all wanted it to. 

Thank you and see you soon ❤️
